{"type":"message","id":"2fd1a5b1","parentId":"a383abde","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:07:49.258Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Locating the Script**\n\nI've pinpointed `src/menu_refresh.py` within the root `src` directory, as the user requested. Now, I must address the Unicode/charmap error before rerunning the script. I'll need to examine the error log to determine the problematic characters and implement a suitable fix to ensure smooth execution.\n\n\n**Reading the Code**\n\nI've located the script and am now immersed in its code to understand its functionality. My goal is to identify potential sources of the Unicode error, particularly within the print statements, so I can apply the appropriate fix before the next run. I'm focusing on the logic that might be creating those pesky special characters.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"read_1771160869253_49","name":"read","arguments":{"file_path":"src/menu_refresh.py"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":90566,"output":137,"cacheRead":7968,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":90703,"cost":{"input":0.181132,"output":0.001644,"cacheRead":0.0015936000000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.1843696}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771160861991}}
{"type":"message","id":"6ca44589","parentId":"2fd1a5b1","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:07:49.277Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"read_1771160869253_49","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"import os\nimport asyncio\nfrom telegram import Bot, BotCommand, BotCommandScopeDefault\n\nasync def main():\n    token = os.getenv(\"TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN\")\n    if not token:\n        print(\"Error: TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN not set.\")\n        return\n\n    print(\"Initializing bot...\")\n    bot = Bot(token=token)\n    \n    commands = [\n        BotCommand(\"dm_start\", \"🚀 Start HFT Trading\"),\n        BotCommand(\"dm_stop\", \"🛑 STOP Trading\"),\n        BotCommand(\"dm_status\", \"📊 Fleet Status\"),\n        BotCommand(\"dm_dashboard\", \"📈 Dashboard\"),\n    ]\n    \n    print(\"Refreshing bot commands...\")\n    try:\n        await bot.delete_my_commands()\n        await bot.set_my_commands(commands, scope=BotCommandScopeDefault())\n        print(\"Commands refreshed successfully.\")\n        \n        # Verify\n        current = await bot.get_my_commands()\n        print(\"Current commands:\")\n        for cmd in current:\n            print(f\" - /{cmd.command}: {cmd.description}\")\n            \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error updating commands: {e}\")\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    asyncio.run(main())\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1771160869275}}
{"type":"message","id":"fa0cbb5a","parentId":"6ca44589","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:07:56.718Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Considering Emoji Interference**\n\nI'm now zeroing in on the emojis. It seems likely they're the root of the problem, specifically in the `print` statement formatting the command descriptions. I'll test removing them from the definitions, as well as the print statements, and see if that resolves the issue.\n\n\n**Fixing the Print Encoding**\n\nMy current thinking leans toward modifying the script itself. Adding `sys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')` is the safest bet for ensuring consistent UTF-8 handling. This should take care of the emoji issue, and resolve any console printing problems in the future.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"edit_1771160876711_50","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"src/menu_refresh.py","oldText":"import os\nimport asyncio\nfrom telegram import Bot, BotCommand, BotCommandScopeDefault\n\nasync def main():","newText":"import os\nimport sys\nimport asyncio\nfrom telegram import Bot, BotCommand, BotCommandScopeDefault\n\n# Force UTF-8 encoding for stdout (Windows fix)\nsys.stdout.reconfigure(encoding='utf-8')\n\nasync def main():"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":91016,"output":268,"cacheRead":87655,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91284,"cost":{"input":0.182032,"output":0.003216,"cacheRead":0.017531,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.202779}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771160869278}}
