{"type":"message","id":"959e7a69","parentId":"058a6722","timestamp":"2026-02-15T13:08:44.777Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Executing the Test Suite**\n\nThe test suite ran as expected, and the sandbox test printed the confirmation of a successful API call despite the expected authentication error. This confirms the `get_balance()` call was properly routed and handled. Furthermore, the logic and hot reload tests also completed successfully.\n\n\n**Verifying the Execution**\n\nThe menu refresh script has been executed. I'll confirm its success or failure, and then identify whether the `TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN` was successfully loaded from the environment, and report back the results. If missing, I'll need to check the configuration and re-run.\n\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"exec_1771160924777_55","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python src/menu_refresh.py"},"thoughtSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":93030,"output":232,"cacheRead":87553,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93262,"cost":{"input":0.18606,"output":0.002784,"cacheRead":0.0175106,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.2063546}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1771160918189}}
